Body:
assert queued_pool.recycle
with queued_pool.acquire() as cxn:
    expired = id(cxn.fairy.cxn)
    cxn.fairy.created_at + queued_pool.recycle
with queued_pool.acquire() as cxn:
    assert expired == id(cxn.fairy.cxn)
    cxn.fairy.created_at -= queued_pool.recycle + 1
with queued_pool.acquire() as cxn:
    assert expired != id(cxn.fairy.cxn)
